    "lyric_eng": "\nGreen leaf of a violet\nCome, turtle dove and tell me\nIs the Danube frozen?\nCan my true love ride across\nWith his three speedy horses?\nOne is black as a raven,\nOne is red as a furnace,\nAnd the horse my love is riding\nHas three feet of ivory.\n"
