    "lyric": "\nKādi ziedi rudzīšam?\nPelēk' ziedi rudzīšam.\n\nKādi ziedi kviesīšam?\nBalti ziedi kviesīšam.\n\nKādi ziedi liniņam?\nZili ziedi liniņam.\n\nKādi ziedi zirnīšam?\nSarkan' ziedi zirnīšam.\n\nKādi ziedi tupeņam?\nZili ziedi, balti ziedi.\n\nKādi ziedi pupiņai?\nRaibi ziedi pupiņai;\n\nTie nebija pupu ziedi,\nTie bij' Dieva pakariņi.\n",
    "lyric_eng": "\nWhat are the blossoms of rye like?\nGrey are the blossoms of rye.\n\nWhat are the blossoms of wheat like?\nWhite are the blossoms of wheat.\n\nWhat are the blossoms of flax like?\nBlue are the blossoms of flax.\n\nWhat are the blossoms of pea like?\nRed are the blossoms of pea.\n\nWhat are the blossoms of potato like?\nThey are blue and white.\n\nWhat are the blossoms of bean like?\nSpotted are the blossoms of bean.\n\nThey are not the blossoms of bean,\nThey are pendants of Dievs.\n"
