    "lyric_eng": "\nAbove the,\nblack, my eyes\nabove the rosebush\nThe partridge builds its nest\n\nThe partridge builds its nest\nGoing and coming, the birds\n\nGoing and coming, the birds\nShaking the rose\n\nShaking the rose\nAnd making the roses fall\n\nMaking the roses fall\nInside the bride's apron\n"
